snippet.title: Living Hope // Jeeva Nambikkai - Angel Seraphs [OFFICIAL MUSIC VIDEO]
snippet.description:
#AngelTV #LivingHope #GoodFriday

Originally performed by Bethel Music (Victory) in English. Translated to Tamil by Angel Seraphs. 

Even with all the sin, chaos and destruction that goes on in this present day, we are reminded of the most important man in history. The son of God who was sent from heaven to earth, to free men from the grips of this world. 

Unlike any other man, He was special.

It has been 2000 years since His death. Which other person in history has been honoured like Him? 

Unlike any other man, He made history. 

He lived as a man, died a gruesome and painful death. A death on the cross that was reserved for murderers and people who steal. But what He did was to steal the hearts of many, to turn their hearts back to the Father. He was mocked, ridiculed and beaten till he could not be recognized. But quietly He muttered, "Father, forgive them".

Unlike eany other man, He suffered. 

He died and His body was put in a tomb. However, on the 3rd day, it was missing. The people wondered, they were afraid. Where did He go? He had risen. Risen to not be a man in history but to be the son of God whose story will be known to all ages throughout eternity. He is risen and He is alive!

He is unlike any other, His name is Jesus and He is our living hope.
